      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR ONYX (2) goes very well here starting eight times for three wins and two minors. Was out of placings last time (28.66) at Mandurah in a OPEN, finishing eighth and beaten 12 lengths. Looks suited here and rates on top. WEST ON GNOCCHI (5) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing seventh (42.83) in a OPEN at this track. Solid record here winning four races. Expected to feature in the finish. LITTLE BOUJEE (1) gave a start after copping a check in running and missed the frame when a 4.5 lengths fifth (30.27) at this track in a Grade 5. Rates a key player and gets chance to atone. SKY REIGN (8) will make his presence felt following a brief layoff.",
